Subject: RE: [EVP-ITC] Re: Paranormal State!?

















LC,



We all know that most of the paranormal community, given the opportunity would choose 

a cheesy tv sci fi ghostie show complete with mirrors, bed sheets and scary sound effects.

over legitimate selfless paranormal research purely for research&#39;s sake.



But if it were not for these type of shows what would all the self proclaimed psychic mediums

and paranormal experts do? crossword puzzles. Don&#39;t you realise that it is shows like this and taps that

have shown that anyone that can afford an emf detector, voice recorder and camcorder with nightshot

and a brand new shinny silver case to carry it all in, can start a paranormal investigating society and

pay their entry fee to get into places like eastern state penn. and collect &quot;REAL&quot; paranormal evidence.



maybe we should try that and stop killing ourselves doing real research and trying to gather legitimate evidence.



come on you guy&#39;s knew I had to throw my 2 cents in!



Bruce








Bruce Halliday 







