I just got to add to FS&#39; point with respect to Paranormal State. 

Anyone notice Ron Milione (TAPS gadget electronics expert) appeared 
on Paranormal State as now a &quot;demon expert,&quot; identifying an EVP on 
the show as a &quot;demon&quot; by the sound of its voice on the recording?

Then I saw Ron on the History Channel&#39;s UFO Hunters as a UFO 
researcher/expert. I&#39;m trying to keep count, but that makes him a 
electronics guru, UFO expert and demonologist! Nice guy, but I think 
he just has a great agent that can get him these &quot;roles.&quot; 

Also, I saw a lady have her home investigated by the Penn State bunch 
on Paranormal State and supposedly in need of their help, then I turn 
the channel and see her as a paranormal investigator on Ghost Hunters 
International! She must have a great agent, too. ;)

LC 

